OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCalls grow for a ban on    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprepayment meter switching 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Calls are growing for energy suppliers 
OL,6, to stop forcibly switching customers   
OL,7, who struggle to pay their bills onto   
OL,8, prepayment meters.                     
OL,10,FCitizens Advice said the practice      
OL,11,Fshould be banned as it saw a sharp rise
OL,12,Fin clients needing crisis support, such
OL,13,Fas emergency grants.                   
OL,15,FMinisters are also preparing to write  
OL,16,Fto regulator Ofgem about the issue.    
OL,18,FIt comes as British Gas said it would  
OL,19,Fstop remotely switching smart meters to
OL,20,Fprepay mode.                           
